\id 1PE - Usan March 2001
\h 1 Pita
\toc1 1 PITA
\toc2 1 Pita
\mt1 1 PITA
\c 1
\s1 1:1,2
\p 
\v 1 Io, ye Pita ye Yisas Munon inubersiau tari eng wonou sarau eb qamb ye maribig yiimuriamorei. End an Qenu wonou munon yamangar eng an ginam qenen wogub iua bunumban Pontus end, ne Galesia end, ne Kapadosia end, ne Esia end, ne Bitinia ai end gagar igoumon end namanimun e gaiar qamb gumotoroum.
\v 2 Qoan ir ininou Tain Qenu animbig ne an wonou yurau igoarar qamb anmaribigorei. Igomurur qau anseara an wonou munon qau igo Munon inubersiau tari Yisas wonou qeru iger anit isuor end an uber igoumon. End wonou qomon uber eng ne oau mein eng anit yab di uya igo.
\s1 1:3-12 Qenu ginamt mismisir igamau eng inoar igo
\p 
\v 3 Qenu ininou Munon inubersiau tari Yisas wonou ur eng igo end in gugum qiumuni ne wot uber qamb igorun. Wo sig borusi mom intoubar ne Munon inubersiau tari Yisas menima igomot der bugamorei. Eng gab-gab ne in munon bubun inmaribigar end in wo qoat uber igumune der inamar iriba.
\v 4 In Qenu wonou ginamt end bebereg igoarar qamb qo maribagatarerei. Mi eng ger me boruburinerei, qenenginob bais me uburinerei, qenen uber ar igoribar eng Qenu ginamt inoar igo.
\v 5 An Qenut oabigari ne wo an qubei an nonogursi igama uber igoumon. Wo anamar iribar qen end anoar igo. Qen sindomund end mi eng dibenara guboumon.
\p 
\v 6 An mi uber end mismisir igoarar. Git apand, see qen pitent ag e igoumon eng qugurau qei-qei gab borumisir igub igoumon.
\v 7 An quguraget igoumon eng Qenu wo aninou oau apand eng warigesi igo. Eng gaiar, mi gagam qenenginob gor qamb igour eng mi uyan nub boruburab igo eng wariges mutet warari bo uberburab igo. Eng gas ende oau apand eng mi gagam gor eng gas ende ue. Oau apand eng sig maieng qenenginob. End ne qugurau ger an oau apand warigesia gab eng end me wot uburab isar, aninou oau apand eng nonogursi ebet igo. An mom nonoguret igo mismisir igamari Munon inubersiau tari eng bo darab an musub unum anbererima mismisiruboumon.
\v 8-9 An munon eng aninou mag qurt me geau ego an wo qenunget igoumon. Ne see gor me gab igoumon ego wot oabig sig borusi mismisir igoumon. Mi end mismisir igoumon eng mi ag et baub qamb mismisir igoumon eng wotanamima. Mi eng aninou oau apand end abari Qenu anmusia igo aninou moui me boruburinerei. Ende aba gab ya uyab igoumon eng qabarit dibes qomorunon eng misue.
\p 
\v 10 Qoan qob gigit qamarau munon mi uber eng gunon end qamamir eng see gaumon eng. Wuri Qenu in bo inqubeieminer qob qanam eng gub qamb ibitiri igurei.
\v 11 Munon inubersiau tari wonou Igomurur qau eng wuriboopuri ten igama ne wo qen mait darab uma ne Qenu unum bereriminer end ete at qebi qamb igurei: “Qen mait deriba a? Wo darab maigas ebeiba a?” ende qamb igurei.
\v 12 Qenu qob eng munon qob gigit qamarau wuriimbigor eng wurinou ue. An see munon qei qob uber eng aninob qamarari igoumon eng wuri ebetemirei. Munon eng qob qamamir eng Qenu wonou Igomurur qau qiribiten imurima der wuriopuri ten igama qob uber eng qanam dibes qamamirei. Munon enger wuri gor qob uber eng igub qamb qenunget igour.
\s1 1:13-25 Qenu in munon qau in maribigor end in munon qei wuriqenungarun
\p 
\v 13 End ne an misir mom musub igub imbig oabig qoat igamari Munon inubersiau tari Yisas anit dibenara guboumon. Mi uber eng end guboumon.
\v 14 An Qenu qob toat igoarar. Qoan an qoyam ue end mi gab oau naget ebet igumanei. See bo qomon eng me abar.
\v 15 Qenu wo munon qau end wonou an maribigor end an munon qau. End an qomon boru mom gitab wogub qau qib igoarar.
\v 16 End Qenu ete qamarei igo: “Ye munon qau end an gor qau igoarar.”
\p 
\v 17 An Qenu qebi qamb: “Tain” qamb igoumon eng. Tain eng wo in munon qen inimbag me inqerei igo, ue. Ininou gari-gari qomon ebet igoun end inqerei igo. End ne ai e see igoun eng ininou ginam qenen ue. End an mom imbig wot igub qib igoarar.
\v 18 Qomon boru eng ebet igoumon eng aninou tonoan qomon animbigumir eng ebet igoumon. Ego Qenu bo anit igub qomon boru eng anit biruet arir ne anba moriamorei. Wo mi ag e boruburab igo eng mai nomon qur qiyo a meimi ger ba, aninou qomon boru end taui qamb arir me biruau, ue.
\v 19 Munon inubersiau tari wonou qeru ai e iriget isuor end gari. Wonou qeru eng mi sig aib. Munon inubersiau tari wo wai sipsip wan yeim git goant qupuam qiyo iam sirigum nob ue gas ende.
\v 20 Wo qoan ir Qenu ai me barsiau igo sarau eng eb qamb wot maribigorei. End anmusierib qamb ne see qas ba dibesia gaumon eng.
\v 21 Wo der umb ne igomot der bogama unum ba dibesier eng gab-gab an Qenut oabig igoumon. Eng wot mismisir qoat igamari bo anamar iriba.
\p 
\v 22 An qob apand eng toat igo ne aninomi maragansiaman end bo misir soagen eng wogub aninou munon banam wuribanamsi igoumon. Eng gag me oboumon, apand oboumon eng wagari ten ende mom igoriner.
\v 23 Eng Qenu wonou qob qenen igo eng qamb ne anseara nani se anbaiau gas ende burab igomot igoumon. End ne see aninou Tain bubun eng wo me uminerei. Wo qenen igomot igo end wonou qob gor qenen gagam igo.
\v 24 End Qenu qob ete qura:
\q1 Munon gugum nam gas ende, ne wuri git baab igour eng nam isar gas ende. Nam isari wogub qen dirigor me igo, bo qand irugor der igo gas ende.
\v 25 Ego Qenu qob wonou qenen igo.
\m Qob uber eng aninob qamarari igub igoumon eng.
\c 2
\s1 2:1-10 Munon Aib Igomot igamau nomon qau
\p 
\v 1 End ne an qomon boru ne qob qetopur qamarau eng mom qabari taisi wagar. Ne munon ger mind irou nob igama gab wot oau me boruburar. Ne mindigar qob qamarau eng gugum wagar.
\v 2 Wogub wau ber inau nub qamb eab igour gas ende eab ne inau uber eng qenen nub igoarar. Inau eng aninou igom meriri nub baraiburab igo end ne Qenu nob uber igoruboumon.
\v 3 An Munon Aib intoubarer eng gaumon eng warigesioumon eng sig uber eng.
\p 
\v 4 End wot isar, wo in igomot igamau eng qanam, nomon gagam gas ende. Munon qei nomon eng boru qamb ba ariramir ego Qenu wo nomon eng sig uber maribigorei.
\v 5 End ne an gor igomot igamau nomon eng gas ende. Munon Aib wot isari munai qau mindaiba. Munai mindat wogub anmaribiga mor isub aninou misirt mian yab wot bigunon eng Yisas Krais wo gab-gab sarau ebetet igamari Qenu animbigiba.
\p 
\v 6 End Qenu qob ete igo:
\q1 Ye nomon ger maribigom eng nomon sig uber. Nomon eng ba qoren unotari yamari mon mom nonogureteriba. Nomon eng ai qaur Saion end bigomei igo. End ne munon ger wot oabig eng naget du qamb wegiba.
\m 
\v 7 An nomon eng wot oabigoumon eng aninou oau uri gas ende wot mismisir igoumon. A munon ger wot me oabig mogirt wab weginer eng ete:
\q1 Nomon eng bo igeser qoren unotari qamb naga mon eng nonoguret igo.
\m 
\v 8 Ne Qenu qob ger ete qura:
\q1 Nomon eng ende igama munon qei yarari wurugumara qiet wogub qoimir yarsiorubour. Munon qei Qenu wonou qob omboarir igour end nomon eng wurugumara yarsiamirei.
\m Qenu wonou qoan qamar gas ende.
\p 
\v 9 An eng Qenu wonou anmaribigor end an wonou munon yurau igoumon. An munon Baraitari wonou munon yurau qau igoumon. End Qenu wonou qomon uber eng abar qamb animbig ebeter eng ete: An qomon qoan eng mom wagari ne wonou begen qenenginob eng anit arirama gaman eng munon qei tumbig wurinob qamarar qamb.
\v 10 Qen qiten an Qenu yurau end me igamau, ego see bo qand an Qenu yurau buroumon. Ne gor, qoan Qenu me an qenungarau, ego see bo qand anqenungar anmoriamorei. Qoan an Qenu antoubar igoar eng qoyam ue, ego see antoubar anmusier eng mom gaumon eng.
\s1 2:11-17 In Qenu wonou iitari sarau oboun
\p 
\v 11 Io, see an e igoumon eng munon ginam ger qunan ibogoub isau nami end an ginam qenen ue. End aninob quraum, an ginam qenen eng Qenu ginamt igo. End an qomon boru mogirt wab wagar. Qomon boru eng aninou misir eng nob yogub igo.
\v 12 Aninou munon yurau ar ginam end isub gab eng qomon qoregen eng qas abar. Wuri der mindigar qob anit qamb gab eng an qomon uber abari animbag wuri Qenu unum bererimari qen end wurit dibeneriba.
\p 
\v 13 An Munon Aibt igub ne ininou munon qomon eng gugum touar. Ne munon baraitari wo gigit igo eng qob qamara igatatar.
\v 14 Gabman munon baraitari igo wonou sarau munon qei imuriamor eng gor qob qamarari toat igoarar. Wuriimurima isumir eng munon ger qomon boru aba gab uyort bigar qamb a munon ger qomon uber aba gab unum bererimar qamb.
\v 15 Qenu an qomon ete abar qamb qenunget igo: Munon qei qomon boru ebet ne qob uber me iruges big igub igour eng wuri an qomon uber toat igamari animbag tumbet igorubour.
\v 16 An qomon gugum eng an songi ugamanei arentor igo. Ego qomon boru eng an me songimau eng gitab igoarar. An Qenu wonou sarau munon igoarar.
\v 17 Igo ne munon gugum wurit igub ne Yisast oabig igour eng nob qibanamsi igoarar. Ende at Qenut igub ne gabman munon Barai inoar igo eng unum bereri igoarar.
\s1 2:18-25 Munon inubersiau tari gitgoan uter war eng in parangaub oboun
\p 
\v 18 Io, an munon ar, munon baraitari qei anoar igamari gab eng an musub igo qob qamarari igatar ne wurinomi eng musub qoat igoarar. Munon uber eng gari qob qamara toaub qamb misir me igar. Ue. Munon uter eng gor qob qamarari toat igoarar.
\v 19 An Qenut igub qomon uber at qib igamari animbag outet anquguragsiari gab eng, an end misir me igar. Qenu anit mismisiriba.
\v 20 Ego qomon boru ebet qib igamari ansumungasiari an bo taui me wurinob yogurunon eng mai obouboumon? Ego qomon uber ebet qib igamari wuri ar aningaramunor eng Qenu annonogursieriba.
\p 
\v 21 Mi eng gagar gugum quraum eng ende abar qamb Qenu anmaribigorei. Qanam eng Munon inubersiau tari eng wo gigit waramari ebet igoar end animbigorei.
\q1 
\v 22 Wo munon qomon boru ger bais me ebet igo ne qob qetopur ger bais me qamara igau.
\m 
\v 23 Ne qob isi wot qamarari wo bo taui me wurinob qamarau. Ne waramir eng gor wo bo taui me wurinob yogorau, sig ue ar. Qenu mi gugum gab qoregen qerei igo eng wonou bo yumusi qamb qoat tug igoai.
\v 24 Munon inubersiau tari eng wonou git goan end ininou qomon boru eng gugum wot ir waga ten umorei. End in qomon boru gugum uburer end bo sabar qomon boru me oboun. Qenen igomot igamau werei end igo qomon qoregen qas ebet igorun. Wo git goan sumungasiamir end anmusuorei.
\p 
\v 25 Qoan an wai sipsip qaararama gas ende igumanei. Ego see bo aninou mor diarari anqubei aninou moui eng nob musiarei.
\c 3
\s1 3:1-7 Munon yamangar qibaumir eng wurinou qob
\p 
\v 1-2 Eng gas ende an yamangar munon nob eng. Aninou munon eng qob qamarari igatar igoarar. Ende abari aninou munon eng an qoregen qib igamari animbag wuri Qenu qob me toat igorunor eng an ende abari animbag wot igubour.
\v 3 Aninou git goan ag eng gari git baab mi goan uber-uber qumani qiyo a tari im ubumimari degen isub qiyo qen big ende me abar.
\v 4 Aninou misir eng git batau gas ende ebet qomon uber eng abari dibent isiner. Isa an yamangar mein igoarar. Ende obounon eng Qenu anqenungariba.
\v 5 Qoan yamangar Qenut oabig ebet igour eng qomon ende ebet igurei. Wuri git baab igour eng umumiagrari qob qamarari igatar qi igour eng wuri git beau gas ende at igurei.
\v 6 Sara wo qomon ende ebet igoai. Umami Abraham qob qamara toat igoar end umamit: “Yonou munon barai,” end wot qamb igoai. An see gor qomon uber ebet ne mi geret me qubig eng an gor Sara tumbigi igoumon.
\p 
\v 7 Yamangar umamimagar, an gor yamangar musub wurinob igoarar. Yamangar wuri git goan sig gagam ue end musub imbig oroar igoarar. Wuri aninob erogori igamari Qenu anseara igomot igoruboumon eng gab wuri im ibag oau mein igo oromar igoarar. Eng an Qenut qebi qamb igoumon eng ar isi isiner qamb.
\s1 3:8-22 Qenen qomon uber toat igumune end in quguragsiorunor eng uber
\p 
\v 8 Ye qob eng sindomund aninob qemeribam eng: an mom qibanamsi igo ne misir gari big munon gugum, aninou ima bain wuriqenungar igoumon gas ende at igoarar. Ende at qiqenunget qimusub igoarar.
\v 9 Munon qei der ansumungasiari gab an gor der taui wurisumungasi qiyo a anit mindigar qob meten qamarari igub an gor der wurit mindigar qob qamb ende me abar. Wuri ende ansiarari ibag an bo taui wurimusub ne Qenut qebi qamarari wuriseara misir igubour. Eng Qenu gigit anit ara yarari ne mi uber anit iyeter end an bo tumbigi munon qei wurimusiarar.
\p 
\v 10 End Qenu wonou qob ete igo:
\q1 Munon wonou qen uber end igomot igorib eng qob boru qamarau end gitab igoriner. Ne qetopur qamarau end gor gitab igoriner.
\v 11 Ne qomon boru eng siningot mogirt wab wogub qomon uber eng ebeib qamb wotrama ebeiner. Ne munon qei wuribanamsiau qomon eng mom tenen igoriner.
\v 12 Eng Munon Aib munon qomon qoregen ende abari eng wuribanamsi igo ne wot qebi qamarari eng igatar igo end. Ne munon ibitiri-ibitiri qomon boru ebet igo eng wo taui sumungasi igo.
\p 
\v 13 An qomon uber eng qeretutnob ebet igorunon eng your ger ansumungasieriba?
\v 14 Ne mai qiyo, an qomon qoregen abari munon qarau qei uyes ansumungasiari gab end me yarimar, misir qebebi me igar. Song Munon Aibt igub mismisir igoarar.
\v 15 Munon inubersiau tari eng ininou Munon Barai qamb mom tenen igoarar. Igamari ne munon qei an qomon uber eng gab an qebi qamarari gab eng aninou tug igoumon eng dibes wurinob qamarar. Wurinob dibes qomorub eng oau mein burab mesenau wurinob qamarar.
\v 16 An Munon oau mein inubersiau tari eng mom tenori igo qenen oau mein igamari animbag wuri aninou qomon uber end ar qob isi anit qamb eng wurinou uyes qininingubour.
\v 17 End in qomon uber ubune uyes inquguragsiari gab eng in Qenut mismisirun. Ne qomon soagen ubune in quguragsiorunor eng uber ue.
\p 
\v 18 Munon in ubersiau tari eng wonomi dui qen gari qas umb wogub ininou qomon boru birueterei. Wo munon sig qoregen uber eng in munon boru uput qamb umb wogub inqubei bayar Qenut wagerei. Wo munangit warub igama waramari umb wogub Igomurur qau ten bo der bugab igomot igo.
\v 19 Wo Igomurur qau ten isub munon boru Noa qent qob qamara me igetet igamau eng umb isub uyort igour eng qob uber wurinob qamarei.
\v 20 Qoan Noa igoar end munon irou qomon boru ebet igour eng Qenu qand me igaramau, wot igunor qamb se oroar igoai. Isi yarab Noa tabin aib mom barsi ugab ne Noa wonou yurau eng munon 8-ende gari tabin erobon end igurei, ya me wurimuarau.
\v 21 Ya qoan qoan ebeter eng see yat anmaragansia an bo wonou yurau end igorunon eng maribig ebeterei. Yat anmaragansi igour eng aninou git goan unun eng birogoniom qamb ue. Aninou misir eng uber igub Yisas munon inubersiau tari umor eng gab-gab Qenut qabari sarog big qamarar qamb.
\v 22 Wo umb wogub igomot der bugab Qenu ginamt irab ur uberegent bugamorei igo Qenu munon yurau enger eng ne Qenu ginamt mi aib-aib a mi qeretutnob igour eng wo gari wuritanami igo.
\c 4
\s1 4:1-6 In munon bubun igeseromun
\p 
\v 1 Munon inubersiau tari wonou gitgoan uter war gas ende an gor qomon eng gari abar. Eng ete: Munon ger wonou gitgoan uter weriner end misir me iginer eng qomon boru eng mom wot uburiba.
\v 2 End ne see wo gitgoan ten igo eng munon qei ebet igour gas ende ebet mi gab oau naget qiyo mi eng gagar me ebet igo eng, wo Qenu mom toat igo.
\v 3 Qoan an qomon boru munon Yisas me imbig ebet igour eng mom toat igumanei. Qomon eng gagar eng ete: yamangar song-song nob qib, a qomon boru abau end oau naget, a ya uter nub qanganget, a mi aib at nub qen dirigor igamau eng. Ne ya uter irou nub qanganget qomon boru abau eng ne Qenu apand qomon biisitet ne aibigau wurit oabig ne abau qomon eng see mom ubura an.
\v 4 Munon Yisas me imbig igour eng see bo an qomon boru eng me toat abari animbag qesigara igo anit mindigarub igour.
\v 5 End ne qen geret wurinou qas qomon eng ebet igour end Qenut dibes qomorubour. Wo munon igom igour eng ne umburiamir eng nob wurinou qomon eng qereimb qamb imbig igo.
\v 6 End ne Qob uber qoan munon umburiamir eng wurinob qamarari igumirei. Wuri gitgoant munon gugum ebet igour gas ende diab qut bigumirei. End qob uber wuri igumir end wurinou moui eng Qenu igom igo gas ende wuri igorubour.
\s1 4:7-11 Qenu mi banam indab igo eng musub qereiomun
\p 
\v 7 Mi gugum uburibar eng qen pi burab igo. End an musub mom imbig aninomi qerei igo qenen Qenut qebi qamb igoarar.
\v 8 Munon banam qiqenungau eng mom qeretutnob ebet igoarar. Qibanamsiau qomon end qomon boru-boru qei gumutumai ne qomon qei wuritanami igo.
\v 9 Munon banam qei qunan yarari ibag musub oromar igoarar. Igo ne bo qi mindigar qob me wurit qamarar.
\v 10 An gari-gari Qenu mi banamsi qo andarerei. Mi eng ar andarer eng an bo taui qamb munon banam wurimusiarar. An ende at igo ne qomon uber eng anit yab di qoa ne Qenu wonou qomon uber eng imbig igoruboumon.
\v 11 Ende ebet ne munon ger qob qanam dibes qamb gab eng, Qenu qob eng qas qemeriner. Ne munon ger wonou munon banam musub gab eng Qenut igub ebeiner. Ende aba ne munon qei wonou qomon uber eng gab ne Munon inubersiau tari Yisas gab-gab Qenu unum ba dibes igorunor. Wo munon barai tari qeretutnob qen e qen e igoriba. Apand.
\s1 4:12-19 In Yisas yurau igo gab eng gitgoan uter iningeriner
\p 
\v 12 Io, mi ger anwarigesieriner eng mut anora uyeriri aningara igoumon gas ende ebeiba. Ende aba igub mi bubun qamb misir qebebi me igub yari abar.
\v 13 Ue, mi eng ende anwarigesieriner eng munon inubersiau tari mi warigesier eng gas ende gab ne mismisirar. Ende ebet ne mi eng anwaga ne Munon Aib unum dibenara gab ne an borusi mismisir ne oau pomaimot igoruboumon.
\v 14 An Munon inubersiau tari eng unumot qib igamari animbag anmerimotar abari ibag an mismisir igoarar. Qenu wonou Igomurur qau qeretutnob eng aninob igo end.
\v 15 Ne aninou erogori end ger der igeig yab qiyo, a mi urim ba qiyo, a qomon boru qei ebet qiyo, a munon qei wurinou qomon qerei wurit qamb qiyo, qomon eng gagar ebet igama waramunor eng uber ue.
\v 16 Ego munon Yisas wonou yurau igama ne end mirinet waramari gab eng me qinininginer. Yisas yurau igo end Qenu unum bereriminer.
\p 
\v 17 Qenu wonou munon yurau wurinou qomon qereiminer eng qo qereiamorei. End ne see ininou qomon eng qereiminer eng isi yarab munon Qenu qob uber igub me oabig igour eng maigas at sindomund uburiba?
\v 18 End Qenu qob ete qura:
\q1 Munon uber eng oromar irib qamb misuet gab eng munon qomon boru ebet igour eng bo maigas at oramar iriba?
\m 
\v 19 End ne munon qei Qenu wonou qomon eng toat qib igamari igaramari gab eng bo me wogunor. Wurinou misir eng mom Qenu baab ten ete igorunor. Wonou inbarsier end qenen mom musub inimbag ten igo, wonou mi uber munon ger wot iyeter eng bais me weginerei.
\c 5
\s1 5:1-4 Sios munon baraitari Qenu munon yurau musub oroar igoarar
\p 
\v 1 See ye aninou munon baraitari eng wurinob qemeribam eng. Ye gor aninob munon baraitari igoum. End yonou magqurt munon inubersiau tari eng waramari gamei. End ne an nob in erogori Qenu wonou qigin eng qen geret diban init arirama guboun. End an munon baraitari sarau e abar qamb aninob qemeribam eng:
\v 2 An munon baraitari Qenu wonou munon yurau eng musub oroar igoarar. Wuri aninou bur wan gas ende aninou wurinob igoumon eng. End munon qei sarau eng abar qamb ansesimoari wuri mag qurt oboun qamb ebet ne aninou misirt qer uriomunon. Ende ue, aninou misirt Qenu wonou sarau abar qamb animbigor eng abar. Ebet sarau taui qur baub qamb misir me igar. Ue, sarau eng mom qenunget abar.
\v 3 An munon baraitari igoumon end misir igub Qenu munon yurau anit wager eng wuribumai aninou qen big ende me abar. Wuri bur wan gas ende an musub oroar igamari wuri animbig antoar igorunor.
\v 4 An ende ebet igorunon eng munon baraitari in gugum inoar igo eng init dibeneriba. Qen end ne mi qenenginob qenen bebereg igoriner eng andariba.
\s1 5:5-11 Ininou gitgoan moui ten Qenu wot duiomun
\p 
\v 5 Eng gas ende gari an wau moi gor. An munon baraitari qob qamarari igatar mi ebet igoarar. An qen bigau qomon eng wogub aninou munon banam qiqenunget igoarar. End Qenu qob ete qura:
\q1 Qenu munon quyai napi qangiribig igour eng wuri agi wogub igo. A munon boru mein igo munon qei qob qamarari igatar igo eng Qenu musub igo.
\m 
\v 6 End ne an mein igo Qenu wonou qeretutnob end igamari wonou qen eng gab anbererimba.
\v 7 Wonou gari anoar igo. End an misir qebebi igub gab eng wot gari igar.
\p 
\v 8 End an musub imbigar, aninou munon qarau Satan wo munon ibag orogar nib qamb bur youn iru isub qib igo.
\v 9 End an mom oabig qoyamet igo omboariramar. Eng an imbigar, aninou munon banam ai gugum igour eng an quguraget igoumon gas ende wuri gor.
\v 10 Ego Qenu qugurau eng anit birueiner eng qanam. End wo munon inubersiau tari, end qen piten qugurau anwaga uberarari bo annonogursieriba. Wo munon inubersiau tari eng gab-gab an wonou ansiarei. End begen qenen bebereg igamau end anamar iriba.
\v 11 Wo munon qeretutnob qen e qen e igoriba. Apand.
\s1 5:12-14 Qob sasam qei
\p 
\v 12 Ye namanimun piten e gumatoroum eng Sailas uben eng ba gumatoroum. Wo ininou munon banam ten. Qob e gumaum eng gab ne Qenu inmusub igo eng qo qamam eng bo imbigar qamb. Qenu wo inubersi igo eng ye mom imbig ne dibes aninob quraum.
\p 
\v 13 Sios munon yurau Babilon e igour eng aninou bainamendimagar gas ende. Wuri gor Qenu wurimaribigor end anit uber quraur. Ne gor Mak wo yonou wau ima gas eng wo gor anit uber qura.
\v 14 An munon banam qiqenungau qomon eng bais me wagar. An Munon inubersiau tari eng mom tenen ete igo oau meinburab igoarar. 
